<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="absurd-adj">absurd <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əbˈsɜːd/    美 /əbˈsɜːrd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-ridiculous">1.★ <strong>荒谬的；荒唐可笑的(ridiculous)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It seems quite absurd to drive for 10 hours just for a 20-minute meeting. 
开车10小时只为参加一个20分钟的会议似乎很荒唐。</p></div></div>